														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2483558">
									

<p>This isn't bad, but I always approach anything with the SPC in it as humor; even at their most serious, their inclusion in a story really does a good job if it's funny even in contrast to serious stuff. The extent of their humor doesn't stop at punching sharks, after all.</p>
<p>This is very dry in that area, so I'm not sure how much I enjoy it. Not bad, but I can't enjoy it. Even <a href="/spc-2615">SPC-2615</a> had humor in it that made me enjoy it, where this I found to be more tight and well-written but not funny on any level. So no-vote.</p>

							</div>

								
					
