														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2483560">
									

<p>There <em>are</em> jokes here: &quot;sharkic&quot;, the implied sharktopusmen, the repetition of Daevites eaten by sharks, &quot;Eaten by sharks is good&quot;, and the implication that the SPC is banned from the Wanderer's Library because the last time they got let in they started punching sharks (probably ornamental aquarium sharks, or patrons)&#8230;</p>
<p>I do admit that they are all both dark and dry. MrWrong's vision of the SPC appealed to me as dark humor, people forced to live inside a universe that was created by a typo.</p>

