<p>Oh yeah, I definitely got the jokes present in the article, but the dryness of it tempered those jokes, for me. I do enjoy the world-building here but it's not something that works for me.</p>
<p>Admittedly, now I'm tempted to write a tale about the Centre dealing with SPC-140 up close and personal&#8230;</p>

