				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164204" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1459578369 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Apr 2016 06:26</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2484104">
									

<p>So for the most part my codenames are semi-random free association:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
BRONZE UPPERCUT: It's a bronze age (originally) book about punches, and it could be a finisher in the Centre's strategic struggle.<br />
CYAN ABYSS: Deep Ones were an inspiration, Charlie Stross uses BLUE HADES for Deep Ones; CYAN is blue, the ABYSS is deep.<br />
GREY WANDERER: One of Gandalf's sobriets. SCP-140-A is kind of like a dark Gandalf.<br />
VENUSBERG: A magical place with amazing stuff and cool people that you can get kicked out of for being an asshole.<br />
GOBLIN CHARIOT: Goblins are magical creatures that you might find in the WL and also sharks. A chariot is a conveyance that you might get driven out on.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
That's pretty much it.
